Project Name: "Trivia Game"
Project Description:
The Trivia Game is a fun and interactive game that challenges players to answer a set of questions in a specific category within a limited time frame. The game will have multiple categories to choose from such as history, science, music, movies, and so on

Features:
A landing page where the player can select a category of their choice to play the game.
The game will have a countdown timer and a score tracker.
Once the player selects a category, they will be presented with a set of questions related to that category.
The player will have a limited amount of time to answer each question.
After answering a question, the player will receive feedback on whether their answer was correct or incorrect.
If the player answers all questions within the time limit, their score will be displayed on the screen.

Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
